    "Given that raw LLM output often suffers from low executability, this layer implements closed-loop pipelines that validate the code and feed error messages back to the model for iterative refinement [56,99,161].",
    "Finally, synergy represents the system-level integration where LLMs are coupled with traditional techniques like SBST [83,133].",
    "This layer aims to combine the semantic understanding of LLMs with the systematic exploration capabilities of traditional tools.Based on the unified taxonomy established above, we structure our analysis around three Research Questions (RQs).",
